{"lemma":"اِبْنَةٍ","slug":"اِبْنَةٍ","root":"ب.ن.#","root_slug":"ب-ن-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ن-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n98","n101","n102","n3370"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A7%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"daughter"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ib.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n98","headword_ar":"اَبَنَهُ","root":"Abn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abonN","text_ar":"اَبْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him an object of imputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspected him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he found fault with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blamed him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cast a foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil, imputation upon him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abanahu bi$aYo'K","text_ar":"اَبَنَهُ بِشَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi$~arK","text_ar":"بِشَّرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as in one copy of the S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixayorKwa$~arK","text_ar":"بِخَيْرٍوَشَّرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, M,) aor. as above, (Lh, S, M, K,) and so the inf. n., (Lh, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him an object of imputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspected him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, accord. to one copy,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of good, and evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^b~nhu","text_ar":"ابّنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixayorK","text_ar":"بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yuw^ab~anu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يُوَبَّنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi$~arK","text_ar":"بِشَّرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is made an object of imputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspected, of good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, * Lh, T [as in the TT; but perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^ab~anu","text_ar":"يُوَبَّنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^obanu","text_ar":"يُوْبَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for it is immediately added,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahuwa maA^obuwnN","text_ar":"فَهُوَ مَاْبُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) when, however, you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yw^bn","text_ar":"يوبن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^obanu","text_ar":"يُوْبَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^ab~anN","text_ar":"يُوَبَّنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] alone, it relates to evil only. (AA, T. [But see 2.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaw^abanu bika*aA","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَوَبَنُ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^ab~anu","text_ar":"يُوَبَّنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is evil spoken of by the imputation of such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, accord. to different copies.) And it is said respecting the assembly of the Prophet,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi AlHuramu","text_ar":"فِيهِ الحُرَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuw^ab~anu","text_ar":"لَا تُوَبَّنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, and so in a copy of the S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA tuw^obanu","text_ar":"لا تُوْبَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in some copies of the S,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Women"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall not be mentioned in an evil manner therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall not have evil imputations cast upon them, nor be found fault with, nor shall that which is foul be said of them, nor that which ought not, of things whereof one should be ashamed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T.) ―         -b2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^b~nhu","text_ar":"ابّنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^obiynN","text_ar":"تَاْبِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found fault with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blamed him, to his face;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he upbraided him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reproached him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["M","S","K","Lh","T"]},{"entry_id":"n101","headword_ar":"اُبْنَةٌ","root":"Abn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A knot in wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a branch;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a staff,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a bow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) [i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the shooting forth of a branch in a bow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) which is a fault therein; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a rope, or cord:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Avl","text_ar":"اثل"},{"kind":"text","text":":)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":10},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ubanN","text_ar":"اُبَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (M,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fault, defect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blemish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K, TA,) in one's grounds of pretension to respect, (T, TA,) and in speech, or language. (M, TA.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)  Particularly The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enormity that is committed with one who is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA^obuwn","text_ar":"مَاْبُون"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enmity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumo A^ubanN","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمْ اُبَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  (S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Between them are enmities."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b5-  Also The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galoSamap","text_ar":"غَلْصَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"epiglottis"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a camel. (M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","M","T","K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n102","headword_ar":"اِبْنَةٌ","root":"Abn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bnY","text_ar":"بنى"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3370","headword_ar":"اِبْنَةٌ","root":"bnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@bonapN","text_ar":"ا@بْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AibonN","text_ar":"اِبْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}